data.title: Release “Violin Summit” by Stuff Smith, Stéphane Grappelli, Svend Asmussen, Jean‐Luc Ponty
data.meta_description: Format: CD, Label: MPS (821 303-2), Barcode: 042282130327, Length: 40:56
data.text:
℗ 1967 MPS Records, W.-Germany

The Violin-Summit was produced by Joachim E. Berendt in collaboration of Südwestfunk Baden-Baden and Radio Basel for Gérard Lüll's Concert series "Jazz im Fauteuil" in Basel/Switzerland, September 30th, 1966
